HREF="http://docbook.org/"
TARGET="_top"
> "La Guía definitiva de
	    DocBook"</A
> de Norman Walsh y Leonard Muellner</P
></LI
><LI
><P
><A
HREF="http://en.tldp.org/HOWTO/DocBook-Demystification-HOWTO/"
TARGET="_top"
>COMO
	- Demistificar Docbook</A
> por Eric S. Raymond. </P
></LI
><LI
><P
>Donald E. Knuth. The TEXbook, Volume A of Computers and
	  Type setting, Addison-Wesley, Reading, Massachusetts, second
	  edition, 1984, ISBN 0-201-13448-9.
	</P
></LI
><LI
><P
><A
HREF="http://www.ams.org/tex/short-math-guide.html"
